About

Welcome to EmpowerAbility Network, your dedicated resource for enhancing the lives of individuals living with disabilities across the United States. At EmpowerAbility Network, we believe in the power of inclusivity, support, and community. Our mission is to empower individuals with disabilities by providing comprehensive resources, advocacy, and personalized assistance to ensure everyone can live a fulfilling and independent life.

Navigating the complexities of living with a disability can be challenging, but you don’t have to do it alone. Whether you’re seeking information on accessible housing, employment opportunities, healthcare services, or educational resources, our platform is here to guide you every step of the way. With a team of passionate advocates and experts, we are committed to breaking down barriers and building a society where everyone can thrive.

Join us in our journey towards a more inclusive and supportive world. At EmpowerAbility Network, we’re not just providing aid; we’re creating a community where everyone has the opportunity to reach their full potential. Explore our resources, connect with our community, and discover how we can help you achieve your goals. Together, we can make a difference.

Child Health Insurance Program (CHIP)

CHIP will provide low-cost health coverage to children in families that earn too much to qualify for Medicaid but cannot afford private insurance

Earned Income Tax Credit (EITC)

Refundable tax credit for low- to moderate-income working individuals and families, particularly those with children
